
= PEDDLE TO THE METTLE

(Tentative name and introduction.)

Besides a table and some friends, you will need: 
 - *Paper and pencils*; index cards or sticky notes preferred
 - *Dice sets*; multiples of d4, d6, d8, d10, d12 (number of sides), typical of tabletop games
 - *Something pleasant to eat and drink*; small pieces of finger food such as berries, nuts or candy preferred. 
 Players who provide the game master with food and drink are to be applauded each session. As a game rule. 

